AWS Global Datacenter
---------------------
- 20 Regions  + 5 soons
- 61 Availability zones
- 158 Edge locations 
- 11 Regional caches
- 130 services.

Regions = Independent Geographic Area
Availability Zones:- Multiple isolated locations and data centers.



